🎯 Objective of Phase 3
The objective of Phase 3 was to build a modular and reproducible ETL (Extract-Transform-Load) pipeline to move raw loan data from CSV format into a structured PostgreSQL data warehouse designed in Phase 2.
This phase converts unstructured raw data into analytics-ready, structured tables aligned with the star schema.
________________________________________
🧠 What We Achieved in Phase 3
We implemented a complete ETL system consisting of:
•	Extract Layer → Load raw CSV
•	Transform Layer → Clean + engineer features
•	Load Layer → Insert structured data into warehouse
•	Modular architecture → Separate Python files
•	Database connectivity using SQLAlchemy
