2️⃣ Transform Phase
Purpose:
Clean, prepare, and engineer features before loading into warehouse.
File: transform.py
import numpy as np

def transform_data(df):
    print("Transforming data...")

    # Convert negative days to actual age
    df["age"] = (df["DAYS_BIRTH"] / -365).astype(int)

    # Handle missing income values
    df["AMT_INCOME_TOTAL"] = df["AMT_INCOME_TOTAL"].fillna(
        df["AMT_INCOME_TOTAL"].median()
    )

    # Remove extreme income outliers (top 1%)
    df = df[df["AMT_INCOME_TOTAL"] < df["AMT_INCOME_TOTAL"].quantile(0.99)]

    # Feature Engineering
    df["loan_to_income"] = df["AMT_CREDIT"] / df["AMT_INCOME_TOTAL"]
    df["emi_burden"] = df["AMT_ANNUITY"] / df["AMT_INCOME_TOTAL"]

    return df
________________________________________
Transformations Performed
✅ Missing Value Handling
•	Filled missing income values with median
✅ Outlier Removal
•	Removed top 1% extreme income values
✅ Feature Engineering
Created new derived features:
•	loan_to_income → credit / income
•	emi_burden → annuity / income
•	age → derived from DAYS_BIRTH
These improve downstream ML performance.
